134
00:14:43,683 --> 00:14:46,652
She dumped snuff juice
on a white man...

135
00:14:46,752 --> 00:14:49,346
on Frank Posey, for Christ's sake.

136
00:14:49,455 --> 00:14:52,788
I wouldn't be surprised
if he flat-out kills her.

137
00:14:52,892 --> 00:14:57,659
You don't mean that.
