535
00:47:28,886 --> 00:47:31,582
<i>A black woman...</i>

536
00:47:31,689 --> 00:47:34,556
With her arm lifted up
and her fist balled out.

537
00:47:34,658 --> 00:47:36,387
<i>Mmm.</i>

538
00:47:36,494 --> 00:47:40,487
<i>Obadiah knelt down on
the wet sand before her...</i>

539
00:47:40,598 --> 00:47:45,558
<i>- and to his shock he heard her voice clear as day.
- Mm-hmm!</i>

540
00:47:45,669 --> 00:47:50,629
- She said, "It's all right. "
- "It's all right. "

541
00:47:50,741 --> 00:47:52,265
<i>- "I'm here. "
- "I'm here. "</i>

542
00:47:52,376 --> 00:47:54,276
<i>"I'll be taking care of you now. "</i>

543
00:47:54,378 --> 00:47:58,712
<i>And Obadiah knew at that moment
