They're coolin' the hive.

682
00:59:11,275 --> 00:59:15,211
That's the sound of 100,000
bee wings fannin' the air.

683
00:59:18,348 --> 00:59:22,808
People have no idea about the complicated life
goin' on inside a beehive.

684
00:59:22,920 --> 00:59:25,184
Here. Let me help you with that.

685
00:59:25,289 --> 00:59:30,158
See, bees have a secret life
we don't know anything about.

686
00:59:41,438 --> 00:59:43,372
<i>Yeah!</i>

687
00:59:44,708 --> 00:59:47,268
<i>Well, if this ain't the livin'end.</i>

688
00:59:47,377 --> 00:59:49,038
Now come over here. You gonna get wet.

689
00:59:49,146 --> 00:59:52,274
Oh, Lord, Lord!

690
00:59:55,152 --> 00:59:59,589
Would you keep it down?

